{"tid":404366,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥失敗被停止活動　日本女團成員「差0.4kg」坐地爆哭","createTime":"2017-09-18T05:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T09:16:42.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1163cafaf6fe7eb3fe995efb45a710f70fa354","tid":404366,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"日本搞怪女子團體「BiS（新生偶像研究會）」作風大膽，活動上大膽讓粉絲頭埋雙乳、摸臀吃豆腐，被調侃是「揉得到的偶像」。成員Pour Lui 3月起參加減肥計畫《DiET or DiE》號稱沒減到目標體重並維持，就要暫停演藝生涯，沒想到她在最新一次測重中，真的因差了0.4公斤，被公司宣布「活動休止」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2801/d2801983.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2801%2Fd2801983.jpg&h=af286c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2801/d2801985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2801%2Fd2801985.jpg&h=694765e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2801/d2801986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2801%2Fd2801986.jpg&h=e7c8620b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Pour Lui差0.4公斤，減肥計畫宣告失敗，她當場坐地爆哭。<br />\n<br />\nPour Lui自3月起開始參加《DiET or DiE》節目，從一開始的51.5公斤、體脂肪30.7%，減到44.6公斤、體脂肪21%，但減肥課程完畢後，第一個月回測發現復胖到47.6公斤、體脂肪22.7%，第二個月雖然稍稍降了1公斤，但體脂肪則是來到24.7%，在最新一集，她接受第3次回測，體重降到45公斤、體脂肪則是20.5%，沒有回到剛上完減肥課時的體重，計畫宣告失敗，得勢不饒人的曼聯最後再有安東尼馬迪爾博得12碼並親自操刀射入，她得知結果後，掩飾不住失望，當唱坐地爆哭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2802/d2802010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2802%2Fd2802010.jpg&h=bb69cb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Pour Lui所屬公司宣布她將暫停演藝活動。<br />\n<br />\nPour Lui所屬公司隨後也真的於BiS官網上發聲明表示，由於她3次回測都未維持當初最瘦時的標準，依照約定，她將暫停演藝活動，「BiS往後的演出，將由6人繼續」。<br />\n<br />\n▼Pour Lui減肥計畫失敗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VF-peWHaR8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVF-peWHaR8Y&d=r%2F0d4hx8Jr8mhOBff1Uf6YM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0802bb78\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VF-peWHaR8Y</a>"},{"pid":"c5223df8860d9c5067b530086a8e8a202908f21c","tid":404366,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"除埋件衫咪夠"},{"pid":"3ee892ed6b188ed605f65f010db6f0565dd58ecc","tid":404366,"uid":122139,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"得勢不饒人的曼聯最後再有安東尼馬迪爾博得12碼並親自操刀射入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79bd38d5edd7439c35f337ebe632049502d6406","tid":404366,"uid":60709,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"計畫宣告失敗，<span style=\"color: red;\">得勢不饒人的曼聯最後再有安東尼馬迪爾博得12碼並親自操刀射入</span>，她得知結果後，掩飾不住失望，當唱坐地爆哭。"},{"pid":"528d0a2ac6c73266835012b9dc824928ed4e326a","tid":404366,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"減咁瘦做咩？之前個張左肥右瘦對比圖已經說明咗男人都係鍾意有肉地"},{"pid":"a8eff42a14de4f38ec91d7fe099a4f4b1a31a013","tid":404366,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbc7e70ff912b90f78a10705680ac5eb89160cf","tid":404366,"uid":33756,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減咁瘦做咩？之前個張左肥右瘦對比圖已經說明咗男人都係鍾意有肉地</blockquote><br />\n有肉地係肉便器   <br />\n瘦先係要黎欣賞"},{"pid":"748b5becc8d4ebd2bc71a9077126b9b1178fc417","tid":404366,"uid":32391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":